{
  "id": "637c9639cd5f5d001def360d",
  "title": "購読とフォローの区別",
  "created": 1669109306,
  "updated": 1669109576,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "637c9639cd5f5d001def360d",
      "text": "購読とフォローの区別",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109576
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fad7",
      "text": "from [Fediverse]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fad8",
      "text": "購読とフォロー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fad9",
      "text": "https://fedibird.com/@noellabo/103298335425285925",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fada",
      "text": ">のえる @noellabo@fedibird.com",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fadb",
      "text": "> #fedibird フォローの代わりに、アカウント購読を試してみませんか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fadc",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fadd",
      "text": "> アカウント購読はフォローと似ていますが、以下の点が異なります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fade",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fadf",
      "text": "> * 購読は相手に通知されません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae0",
      "text": "> * 購読していることは、相手が知ることはできません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae1",
      "text": "> * 連合タイムラインに流れている、公開投稿だけを受け取ります",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae2",
      "text": "> * フォローに承認が必要なアカウントを、承認不要で購読できます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae3",
      "text": "> * 購読を解除しても相手に通知されません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae4",
      "text": "> * 何を購読しているか、いくつ購読しているか、他の人に見えません",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae5",
      "text": "> * 購読者へは配送が不要のため、サーバとネットワークの負荷が軽い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae6",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae7",
      "text": "> このことにより、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae8",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085fae9",
      "text": "> * フォローにともなう、相互関係・人間関係への配慮が不要です",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faea",
      "text": "> * 未収載・フォロワーのみなど、相手が積極的に公開していない投稿を目にせずに済みます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faeb",
      "text": "> * 承認が必要なアカウントを無理にフォローしなくて済むので、お互い楽に運用できます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faec",
      "text": "> * サーバやネットワークにあまり負荷をかけずに済むため、遠慮なく購読を増やせます",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faed",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faee",
      "text": "> お薦めの使い方",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faef",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faf0",
      "text": "> * 最初は購読で始め、関係が深まったらフォローに移行する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faf1",
      "text": "> * 興味を持ったら、まずは購読して、あとで整理する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669109306,
      "updated": 1669109306
    },
    {
      "id": "637c9639aff09e000085faf2",
